My painting process from the very beginning. Part 1:
In this stage, I stretch the canvas, prime it with my favorite primer from @mhpaints (available in a variety of colors), and sketch using a grid. Stay tuned for part 2! 🤗🌸

#artist #artistoninstagram #artstudio #artistinstudio #mhpaints #realismtoday
#paintingprocess #paintingprogress #drawing #realisticdrawing #paintingoncanvas #womanartist #figurativepainting #figurativeart #kunst #drawings #

Part 2. In the first part, I prepped the canvas and sketched. Now, I’m diving into the fun stuff - starting with the eyes and working my way out. I absolutely love this stage, especially when playing with all the skin tones and colors. And, of course, I’m using my favorite @mhpaints 🧡♥️🩵Getting ready for @laartshow next year with @arcadiagallery! 🥳🍾⭐️

The gallery have released two new prints for sale, you can see both in the link in bio-  @galleriramfjord 

A giclee is a printed reproduction of an original painting. The painting is photographed by a professional photographer and proof prints are made. When the artist is happy with the result, an edition is being made by using a specialized high resolution inkjet printer on high quality cotton paper.
The prints are in a limited edtion of 15, signed and numbered by the artist.

This competition is not in any way sponsored, promoted, managed or linked to Instagram.

Hello, everyone! I hope you're all doing well. I try to make my posts interesting and fun, but sometimes, there have to be ones like this... 🫢 I'm pretty tired of this issue.

Recently, there have been multiple fake accounts impersonating me, attempting to scam some of you. And it’s not just one account, but MANY. It's disheartening to witness this happening, but I want to let you know that @kesjatabaczuk is my ONE and ONLY Instagram profile.

I've reported these scammers numerous times, and I deeply appreciate those of you who have done the same. However, the issue persists, with new accounts popping up each time one is removed.

I was inspired by @ruthfittonportraits , who faced a similar situation, and decided to take this step to confirm my identity.

Swipe right to see some of these fake accounts that have been causing this issue and report them if you have a moment 😜. Thank you for your support and understanding!🌸🌸🌸

#artisticidentity #realKesja #verifiedaccount  #verifiedprofile #artisticcommunity  #reportscammers #fightfakeaccounts
